ative setup\nconsisting of a pure CsI crystal matrix read by UV extended Hamamatsu MPPC's is\nalso presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Aug 2016 23:11:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-17"}
