ation. We illustrate our approach in an industrial example which\nshows that the formal semantics of requirements relations, changes and traces\nenables the identification of candidate architectural elements with the\nreduction of some false positive impacts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Aug 2016 10:48:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-10"}
